exceptions.tactic: pose proof (cohK W1 (W1 \+ W2) K pf) as HcohK.
exceptions.exn: In environment W1, W2 : world K : hooks pf : injects W1 (W1 \\+ W2) K Hvalid : valid (W1 \\+ W2) The term "W1" has type "world" while it is expected to have type "injects ?U ?V ?K".

original: intros Hvalid. pose proof (cohK W1 (W1 \+ W2) K pf) as HcohK. rewrite HcohK in *. apply joinC. rewrite (joinC (inj_ext pf) (Unit, K)) in HcohK. apply dom_prec with (dom W1 \+ dom (inj_ext pf) \+ K). - apply validL in Hvalid. apply Hvalid. - apply validL in Hvalid. rewrite <- HcohK. apply Hvalid. - intro x. rewrite !domUn. rewrite !domUn. destruct (x \in dom W1); simpl; reflexivity.
